{"tid":932240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐綺陽：2019年就好像一部失速列車，大家能逃的快逃","createTime":"2018-12-07T15:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T16:13:49.000Z","uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5185bbac70c7777e58ebd62aaf1069e2c8ff703f","tid":932240,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"根據《三立新聞網》報導，她透露了2019年個過度年，充滿了大變動，而土冥合相，甚至比2018年還要靠近，也導致了每個人都有自己的挑戰。她說：「大家都同搭一部失速列車，速度過快，全車都會恐慌，很多人會被某些事打敗或很成功，就是很兩極化，然後這幾年在硬撐有名的大公司或機關，會撐不住倒下，我勸大家，能逃的快逃。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好迷信星座，要堅守原地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我走先"},{"pid":"e7519a24bc07bc285dfdbd1915e1b7b13ca60e44","tid":932240,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"腦魔：drop to zero <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2734bf3ec3a01948bd155bce189360bab748f19e","tid":932240,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"睇返上年個post<br />\n<br />\n2018全球經濟將破滅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/502158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/502158</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全球就唔知<br />\n大陸同香港已dead"}]}